{"lemma":"سَراحِ","slug":"سَراحِ","root":"س.ر.ح","root_slug":"س-ر-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ر-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سَراح","root":"سرح","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19515","n19520"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"release","examples":[{"text":"وجاء إطلاق سراحهم وفق البيان، نتيجة «عملية مشتركة بين شعبة المعلومات في قوى الأمن الداخلي والأمن العام (اللبناني) والمخابرات العراقية».","english":"And their release came, according to the statement, as a result of “joint operation between the Information Division of the Internal Security Forces and the General Security of Lebanon and the Iraqi intelligence.”"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sa.raːħ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19515","headword_ar":"سَرَاحٌ","root":"srH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasoriyHu AlmaroA^api","text_ar":"تَسْرِيحُ المَرْاَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) [i. e., a subst.] signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dismissal"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a wife"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by divorcement:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in xxxiii. 28 [where it is used as a quasi-inf. n., as it is also in verse 48 of the same chap.]:) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalaAqN","text_ar":"طَلَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firaAqN","text_ar":"فِرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divorcement"},{"kind":"text","text":"explicitly. (L.) ―         -b2-  [And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dismissal"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a general sense. Hence,] it is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~araAHu mina Aln~ajaAHi","text_ar":"السَّرَاحُ مِنَ النَّجَاحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dismissal is a part of the accomplishment of one's want"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, A, L;) meaning, when thou canst not accomplish a man's want, make him to despair; for thy doing so will be in his estimation an act that will stand him in lieu of thy helping him to accomplish it: (S, L: [in some copies of the former, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^ayoy^isohu","text_ar":"فَاَيْيِسْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", we find"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA=yasotahu","text_ar":"فَا=يَسْتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or it is applied to a man who does not desire to accomplish the want [of another]; and means, it behooves thee to make him to despair if thou accomplish not his want. (Meyd. [See a similar prov. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araAHN","text_ar":"شَرَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Haste, ex-"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1346},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pedition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"promptness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ease:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifoEalo *`lika fiY saraAHK warawaAHK","text_ar":"اِفْعَلْ ذٰلِكَ فِى سَرَاحٍ وَرَوَاحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) i. e. (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do thou that in a state of ease"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and A and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwH","text_ar":"روح"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and rest."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A in that art.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saraAHi","text_ar":"سَرَاحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[indecl.] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTaAmi","text_ar":"قَطَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [app. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick and easy in pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~uruHu","text_ar":"السُّرُحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] the name of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain horse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]},{"entry_id":"n19520","headword_ar":"سَرَّاحٌ","root":"srH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[probably meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick and easy in pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suruHN","text_ar":"سُرُحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] the name of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a horse of El-Mohallak Ibn-Hantam."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}